{"tid":1904560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國2月製造業PMI大跌至35.7","createTime":"2020-02-29T16:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T16:59:03.000Z","uid":138609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"790704b53ccdb370600fe96332b57877330b99c6","tid":1904560,"uid":138609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:56:34.000Z","msg":"受新型冠狀病毒肺炎(俗稱武漢肺炎)疫情衝擊，中國製造業活動明顯收縮。國家統計局公布，2月份，中國製造業採購經理指數(PMI)為35.7%，按月下降14.3個百分點，亦顯著低於預期的46。<br />\n<br />\n官方數字都跌得咁慘<br />\n實際數字沒有最差只有更差<br />\n支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0af5f25485aaffa9dd73987ab9f110743ff19b","tid":1904560,"uid":23445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:58:27.000Z","msg":"因空氣污染而死既人大跌<br />\n人口不減反升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739de27c2e8f9d5b653121f779b311a69667af84","tid":1904560,"uid":322670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"實際應該3.57啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}